contentrichtext.text: {{Distinguish|Lake Forest (disambiguation)}} '''Forest Lake''' may refer to: ==Places== In '''Australia''': * [[Forest Lake, Queensland]], a master planned community within the city of Brisbane in Queensland In '''New Zealand''': * [[Forest Lake, New Zealand]], a suburb of Hamilton In the '''United States''': * [[Forest Lakes, Arizona]] * [[Forest Lake, Arizona]] (Navajo Nation) * [[Forest Lake, California]], an unincorporated community in Lake County * [[Forest Lake, Illinois]], a census-designated place in Lake County * [[Forest Lake, Michigan]], an unincorporated community in Alger County * [[Forest Lake, Minnesota]], a city in Washington County * [[Forest Lake Township, Susquehanna County, Pennsylvania]] * [[Forest Lake Camp]], a summer camp in upstate New York. == Schools == * [[Forest Lake Academy]], Orlando, Florida, USA * [[Forest Lake College]], Queensland, Australia * [[Forest Lake State High School]], Queensland, Australia {{geodis}}
